{"tid":650583,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[MCU] 復仇者聯盟3 : 無限之戰Avengers : Infinity War 劇透討論區 (15)","createTime":"2018-05-02T12:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:43.000Z","uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7623790a96228bc9ffe42c32679154f3b8f0a9","tid":650583,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">MCU = Marvel<br />\n唔洗再拎火影套垃圾嚟比 thanks<br />\n已經聽咗條戇鳩&quot;芝士壽司&quot;loop 咗百鳩幾次<br />\n仲自製Q&amp;A 扮置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎繼續討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"6a5faacb8d1c875a98f58c43d59ca4a49679a538","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A1 ［彩蛋 、Doctor Strange 篇］<br />\n<br />\n- 片尾彩蛋個logo係《驚奇隊長》Captain Marvel，套戲下年出，內容係講90年代<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/192405_d7cb843cc2653be094f7176825d4567d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F192405_d7cb843cc2653be094f7176825d4567d.png&h=0da1a963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://insidepulse.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Brie-Larson-as-Captain-Marvel-in-recolored-fan-uniform.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finsidepulse.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2FBrie-Larson-as-Captain-Marvel-in-recolored-fan-uniform.jpg&h=b8d8a932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://dailypicdump.com/media/20180413/loki-lowkey-brie-larson.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdailypicdump.com%2Fmedia%2F20180413%2Floki-lowkey-brie-larson.gif&h=b7d83c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n- 彩蛋Nick fury得一隻眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/191955_31b9a46fe7f600906be7931a8a1d247f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F191955_31b9a46fe7f600906be7931a8a1d247f.png&h=efbd7783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 臨尾死人係random (都有人估係 Doctor Strange 係時間寶石度做手腳)<br />\n<br />\n- Doctor Strange 個同伴叫 Wong，而唔係Wang啊，佢最後去返守護聖所<br />\n<br />\n- Doctor Strange 睇到 14,000,605個未來，理論上係睇曬所有斬手斬腳、制止Starlord打鳩Thanos既結局都仍然係輸。<br />\n<br />\n- 點解Doctor Strange 打Thanos 唔出ring斬手斬腳? <br />\n坊間眾說紛紜，唔好駁 費事比人屌 （如同Save marhta一樣）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- Thanos識唔識用同一隻魔法睇未來暫時唔知，Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU)入面只係得Doctor Strange 1 (2016)入面既古一Ancient One（Doctor Strange師傅），同埋Avengers 3: Infinity War (2018)既Doctor Strange識用。<br />\n<br />\n- 點解Doctor Strange唔可以好似Doctor Strange 1 (2016)咁用Infinity time loop困住Thanos? <br />\n原因係Doctor Strange 係Doctor Strange 1 (2016)用time loop 嘅時候，係喺超越時間嘅Dark Dimension<br />\n因為Dormmamu 係超越時間嘅存在，會感受到一直困喺同一個時間。而如果係Infinity war 用time loop ，其實係冇意義<br />\n因為Thanos 本身唔係超越時間，佢感知唔到自己困喺同一個時間，做唔到威脅Thanos嘅效果"},{"pid":"4b68afbb44ce36565a645a9d380978961b6667d6","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A2 ［蟻俠 、鷹眼 篇］<br />\n<br />\n- Avengers 3: Infinity War (2018)中間有提蟻俠同箭佬俾人軟禁緊<br />\n<br />\n- 《蟻俠2：黃蜂女現身》（28/6/2018 上畫） 係講蟻俠佢地逃走緊，時間係Captain America 3 : Civil War (2016)後、Avengers 3 : Infinity War (2018)前<br />\n（1/5/2108新出trailer)<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pehJPC_GasU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpehJPC_GasU&d=RTzJzPmp%2FTudvMp1PquxlJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a74916c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pehJPC_GasU</a><br />\n<br />\n- Avengers 4 (2019) 片場相流出100%有蟻人出場<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/161713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F161713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1cbcbd6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69e43ec87d895db50d312cff7c1cd13f7908c7f5","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A3 ［雷神、Hulk、美國隊長  篇］<br />\n <br />\n- 雷神新武器stormbreaker 內置有傳送功能bifrost (彩虹橋)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/131547_40d9c2c2a9bfb73b81ee000d15b0d4f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F131547_40d9c2c2a9bfb73b81ee000d15b0d4f6.jpg&h=68cf5fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n- Banner 同 Black Widow 係 Avengers 2: Age of Ultron (2015)  時拍過拖但之後分開一段時間，再見返無野講所以尷尬<br />\n（題外話： Black Widow係Captain America 2: The Winter Soldier (2014)時期，佢同鷹眼拍緊拖，戴住箭形頸鍊）<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.comicplanetculture.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/172/2014/06/Black-Widow-Arrow-Necklace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.comicplanetculture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F172%2F2014%2F06%2FBlack-Widow-Arrow-Necklace.jpg&h=eb611123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- Trailer 度有Hulk 作戰係呃人去睇戲嘅手段，戲入面無<br />\n<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F010.jpg&h=caebbd5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- Hulk係俾Thanos打輸左唔敢出黎柒，重有地球人唔鍾意佢，所以佢唔肯出黎。<br />\n<br />\n- 摺機手提電話係 Captain America 3 : Civil War (2016) 最後美國隊長寄比Tony 緊急時搵對方<br />\n<img src=\"https://peliculasdecomics.files.wordpress.com/2017/11/avengers-infinity-war-tony-flip-phone.jpg?w=1040\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpeliculasdecomics.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F11%2Favengers-infinity-war-tony-flip-phone.jpg%3Fw%3D1040&h=80e0bb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n- 懷疑美國隊長超級血清開始減弱，身體日漸消瘦<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.gamespot.com/uploads/original/1557/15576725/3366874-captain-america-chris-evans-nomad-rumors-1075864-1280x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.gamespot.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F1557%2F15576725%2F3366874-captain-america-chris-evans-nomad-rumors-1075864-1280x0.jpeg&h=1b849484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac5b225d2ce6e3b5ce43495d9603f68456b01c32","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A4 ［Vision 、Thanos、Ironman   篇］<br />\n <br />\n- Vision 被亡刃(Corvus Glaive)用長柄刀（可切開atom）偷襲，所以Vision 復修唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sideshowtoy.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Corvus_Glaive_Earth-616_from_New_Avengers_Vol_3_8_001-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sideshowtoy.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FCorvus_Glaive_Earth-616_from_New_Avengers_Vol_3_8_001-1.jpg&h=63a5db93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 漫畫入面其實Thanos係為左追死亡女神DeathDeath，先要收集石頭再消滅一半人口<br />\nThanos經常想毀滅所有生命之類的，其實也是為了送禮物給女神... <br />\n這位Death女神一般都是黑紫色兜帽的骷髏形象。<br />\n但似乎Thanos失敗之後就被拋棄了，反而是因為Deadpool經常有各種瀕死經歷，所以導致話Deadpool也迷戀上了Death。<br />\n就有了倆人爭風吃醋之類的橋段，但似乎Death沒有明確表示過鍾情哪一個就是了，所以佢兩個應該都做兵居多。<br />\n<img src=\"http://nerdist.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Deadpool-Thanos-Death-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnerdist.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2FDeadpool-Thanos-Death-3.jpg&h=92242e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1461965488i/18936120._SY540_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gr-assets.com%2Fimages%2FS%2Fcompressed.photo.goodreads.com%2Fhostedimages%2F1461965488i%2F18936120._SY540_.jpg&h=98d2ce3f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- Thanos 由Avengers 1 (2012) 就開始留意地球英雄，所以識 Tony Stark 同知道粒mind stone係 Vision 度<br />\n<br />\n- 點解Ironman 比Thanos 直插一刀都好似無事？<br />\n依家Ironman套納米裝甲已經入骨，所以唔中要害，應該好快復修<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.gamelib.com.br/static/_versions/uploads/assets/maio-2013/extremis2_content.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.gamelib.com.br%2Fstatic%2F_versions%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2Fmaio-2013%2Fextremis2_content.jpg&h=54ddc6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://im.ziffdavisinternational.com/ign_tr/screenshot/default/sim3_efzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim.ziffdavisinternational.com%2Fign_tr%2Fscreenshot%2Fdefault%2Fsim3_efzs.jpg&h=1f23cace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.monkeysfightingrobots.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Cyborg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monkeysfightingrobots.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FCyborg.jpg&h=2e448efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\np.s. 愈來愈似cyborg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb82cce79526d663c0cd79cf36e37158ac1280a4","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"置頂Q&amp;A5〖Marvel 不願面對的事情1〗【懷疑Avengers3被抄劇本？】<br />\n<br />\n＊有冇發現今集Avengers3同日本某一套富爭議性動漫既內容多處相似？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n【1】 Thanos ＝斑? &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n＞＞角色能力<br />\n・六粒石 ＝ 六道之力<br />\n・(i) 吸敵人攻擊，再射番比人（餓鬼道／宇智波反彈）<br />\n・(ii) 彈走人（神羅天征）<br />\n・(iii) 拉D星球落黎攻擊人（地爆天星）<br />\n・(iv) 空間轉移（黄泉比良坂 ）<br />\n・(v) 用幻術（伊邪那岐）<br />\n・(vi) 操控生死（外道&middot;輪迴天生之術）<br />\n<br />\n・呢招似唔似 求道玉 ／螺旋丸？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/224039_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F224039_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=fbfaaf89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n・ 全啪五隻手指 ＝穢土轉生：解？<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/47917337b84219ad397378d93cfe12c4/tumblr_p80vwsaven1rwdvuco5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F47917337b84219ad397378d93cfe12c4%2Ftumblr_p80vwsaven1rwdvuco5_250.gif&h=392604e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＞＞角色描寫<br />\n・要殺左至親，先可以得到soul stone （殺兄弟 升級萬花筒寫輪眼呢）<br />\n<br />\n・上幾集Avengers 1, Thanos派手下去收集infinity stones，但被avengers打走（斑指示組織曉去收集尾獸，被嗚門一行人等打敗滅團，最後今集要老人家親自出馬。）<br />\n<br />\n・Thanos搞咁多野，原意係想世界和平，balance世界資源，只係d村民唔理解。（斑發動無限月讀，同樣為了世界和平）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【2】 Vision ＝人柱力? &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n・Superheros 為左保護Mind stone 持有者Vision，就送佢入黑人秘密基地匿，其他superheros就出去守住保護罩 （第四次忍界大戰前夕 村民保護嗚門，同樣送嗚門入秘密基地匿埋，怕九尾被搶走，最後個傻仔自己走出黎。Mind stone 被抽走，「人柱力」就會無命，係咪好似呢？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【3】 奇異博士  &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n・影分身？<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/e1a50f97f0f2d47fc5857deecddae45f/tumblr_p7xoyeZwTz1vk745jo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fe1a50f97f0f2d47fc5857deecddae45f%2Ftumblr_p7xoyeZwTz1vk745jo1_400.gif&h=30483301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n・神威？<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3orif7N2qBUUJ2hUK4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3orif7N2qBUUJ2hUK4%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e525937c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n・（回帶番Doctor Strange獨立電影）Doctor Strange打Dormammu使用Time loop一幕，似唔似 鼬太知發動「伊邪那美」付兜？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【4】 雷神＝佐助？ &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n・全族死清光 ＋ 睇住兄弟被殺 <br />\n・重生後獲得USB眼睛<br />\n・雷遁<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/9zZKwOtDCN3N4qR2CN/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9zZKwOtDCN3N4qR2CN%2Fgiphy.gif&h=70fa3cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【5】Mantis螳螂女 傳心術 = 山中一族 身心轉換術？&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ca_qMTvVSfE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fca_qMTvVSfE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=5415449e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【6】Hulk ＝木葉蒼藍野獸？&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n・復仇者聯盟最強體術使用者-Hulk 被滅霸Thanos輕易打敗，之後再無出場。<br />\n<img src=\"http://fanboygaming.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/thanos-vs-hulk-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffanboygaming.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fthanos-vs-hulk-800x445.jpg&h=357641c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【6】 Black widow突然剪短頭髮，係咪好似港女櫻呢？  <br />\n<br />\n【7】 wakanda 士兵／外星狗狗＝白絕？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/210701_8b26f939898ddc93aa5c63dff7637f34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F210701_8b26f939898ddc93aa5c63dff7637f34.jpg&h=482613d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【8】日本仔抄野早有前科，回帶番Captain America 2 : The Winter Soldier (2014)<br />\n入面既打鬥場面，後來被日本某動畫十足十抄過黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201709/26/hh5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201709%2F26%2Fhh5.gif&h=142ba718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201709/26/hh4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201709%2F26%2Fhh4.gif&h=d881a786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【9】Avengers 3以「鋪排十年顛峰之作」作宣傳賣點；日本某漫畫疾X傳（2007-2017) ，又係鋪排左十年！？<br />\n<br />\n｜<br />\n｜<br />\n｜<br />\n｜<br />\n｜<br />\n<br />\n【延伸討論】<br />\n！好怕下一集Thanos會學 長門個on9仔被嘴遁， 幫所有人復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n！下集Antman幫手穿越時空，似唔似臨死既帶土用神威幫主角帶路？"},{"pid":"621055ee9e31fb2b4f14695090252b278282f479","tid":650583,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"注意事項：[MCU]討論區方仗<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">瓦坎達皇后(喪夫)（#100236）</span></span></strong>份人<br />\n<br />\n＊入黎劇透post，都係想討論復仇者聯盟3，私人因怨私下解決就好了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/84/NVk.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130217060858\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F84%2FNVk.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130217060858&h=02f0f221&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}